quran[7]{c,v,t}:
  107,1,"F pa yã ned ning sẽn yagsd-a Rolbã rɑɑrã?"
  107,2,"Yẽ la ned ning sẽn tusd kɩɩb tus-kεgenga."
  107,3,"A leb n pa pirsd ne nimbãan-ned rɩlgr ye."
  107,4,"Rẽnd wɩɩbd be ne pʋʋsdba."
  107,5,"Pʋʋsdb nins sẽn maand yam yaal-yaal ne b Pʋʋsgã."
  107,6,"Neb nins sẽn yãngd nebã."
  107,7,"La b mongd sõngr teedo."
